Value Required zone (\S+)
Value active (active)
Value target (\S+)
Value icmp_block_inversion (yes|no)
Value interfaces (\S+)
Value sources (\S+)
Value services (\S+)
Value ports (\S+)
Value protocols (\S+)
Value masquerade (yes|no)
Value forward_ports (\S+)
Value source_ports (\S+)
Value icmp_blocks (\S+)
Value rich_rule (.+)

Start
  ^${zone}( \(${active}\))?
  ^  target: ${target} -> Record
  ^  icmp-block-inversion: ${icmp_block_inversion} -> Record
  ^  interfaces: ${interfaces} -> Record
  ^  sources: ${sources} -> Record
  ^  services: ${services} -> Record
  ^  ports: ${ports} -> Record
  ^  protocols: ${protocols} -> Record
  ^  masquerade: ${masquerade} -> Record
  ^  forward-ports: ${forward_ports} -> Record
  ^  source-ports: ${source_ports} -> Record
  ^  icmp-blocks: ${icmp_blocks} -> Record
  ^  rich rules: -> RichRules

RichRules
  ^${rich_rule} -> Record
  ^\s*
